Description: Seaway 7 ASA is a Norway-based company, which is active in the offshore Renewables Energy industry. The Company engages in delivery of fixed offshore wind projects, offering standalone or integrated foundation, offshore substation, submarine cable and wind turbine generator installation services through various contracting models. Seaway 7 offers the following services: wind turbine generator installation, offshore foundation installation, offshore substation installation, offshore submarine cable installation and heavy transportation for the renewables sector. With the group's engagem in project management, engineering, procurement, and fabrication, as well as fleet and specialist technologies, it can deliver services through a comprehensive array of contractual structures including Engineering, Procurement, Construction and Installation (EPCI), Transportation and Installation (T&I) and Balance of Plant (BoP).
